  <lyrics>[V1]
 Diosaru yupaychañawa, jichhürojja jupanquiwa.
 Sojjtürojja tucutawa, Cristoruya k'ochuñáni.
 
[C]
 Jichhürojja Diosanquiwa
 Kharürusa jupanquiwa;
 Waquisiw yupaychañasa,
 Tatituna utapana. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Sojjturonjja almasasa sinti t'uqhartataraquiw;
 Jichhürojja kamañáni, Tatituna utapana.
 
[V3]
 Cristo Kollana Awquejja marcamarojj uñtanimay
 Mayisipjjsmawa Awquejja, ist'anipjjaquitay Tata.
 
[V4]
 Jacanajjansa Dios Tatay janiwa asquichasipcti,
 Cristo Kollana Awquejja; yanapt'asipjjaquitaya.
 
 </lyrics></song>